      "position": [-1000, 300],
      "notes": "operation = 'get' | 'update' | 'search'. Yeh workflow poore system ki single source of truth hai CRM read/write ke liye — koi bhi doosra workflow seedha Google Sheet ko touch nahi karta, sab isi se guzarte hain."
